{"kanda":6,"sarga":101,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"तस्मिन्प्रतिहतेऽस्त्रेतुरावणोराक्षसाधिपः ।क्रोधं च द्विगुणंचक्रेक्रोधाच्चास्त्रमनन्तरम्","trans":"Missile being counteracted, Ravana, the king of Rakshasas, doubled the army later in anger.","words":[{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"by that"},{"d":"अस्त्रे","m":"missile"},{"d":"प्रतिहते","m":"counteracted"},{"d":"राक्षसाधिपः","m":"king of Rakshasas"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"द्विगुणम्","m":"doubled the army"},{"d":"क्रोधम्","m":"angry"},{"d":"क्रोधात्","m":"in anger"},{"d":"अनन्तरम्","m":"later"},{"d":"अस्त्रम्","m":"missile"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"मयेनविहितंरौद्रमन्यदस्त्रंमहाद्युतिः ।उत्सृष्टुंरावणोभीमंराघवायप्रचक्रमे","trans":"Highly effulgent Ravana used another terrific missile, presided over by Rudra, produced by Maya.","words":[{"d":"महाद्युतिः","m":"highly effulgent"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"मयेन","m":"by Maya"},{"d":"विहितम्","m":"manifested"},{"d":"रौद्रम्","m":"presided by Rudra"},{"d":"अन्यत्","m":"another"},{"d":"अस्त्रम्","m":"missile"},{"d":"राघवाय","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"उत्सृष्टुं","m":"taking"},{"d":"प्रचक्रमे","m":"used"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"ततःशूलानिनिश्चेरुर्गदाश्चमुसलानि च ।कार्मुकाद्दीप्यमानानिवज्रसाराणिसर्वशः","trans":"Then from his bow issued forth all over flaming tridents, maces, and iron bars like thunderbolt.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"कार्मुकात्","m":"with bow"},{"d":"वज्रसाराणि","m":"like the thunderbolt"},{"d":"दीप्यमानानि","m":"flaming"},{"d":"शूलानि","m":"trident"},{"d":"गदाश्च","m":"mace"},{"d":"मुसलानि च","m":"iron bar"},{"d":"निश्चेरुः","m":"issued forth"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"मुद्गराःकूटपाशाश्चदीप्ताश्चाशनयस्तथा ।निष्पेतुर्विविधास्तीक्ष्णावाताइवयुगक्षये","trans":"Several kinds of sharp multitudes of weapons and flaming thunderbolts issued forth like gales at the time of universal destruction.","words":[{"d":"तीक्ष्णाः","m":"sharp"},{"d":"मुद्गराः","m":"clubs"},{"d":"कूटपाशाश्च","m":"multitudes"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"अशनयश्च","m":"thunderbolts"},{"d":"युगक्षये","m":"at the end of universal destruction"},{"d":"वाताःइव","m":"like gales"},{"d":"निष्पेतुः","m":"issued forth"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"तदस्त्रंराघव्श्रीमानुत्तमास्त्रविदांवरः ।जघानपरमास्त्रणगान्धर्वेणमहाद्युतिः","trans":"Glorious Raghava, who is the best of those proficient in the use of missiles endowed with great splendour, neutralized that missile (of Ravana) with the missile presided over by Gandharvas.","words":[{"d":"श्रीमान्","m":"glorious"},{"d":"उत्तमास्त्रविदम्","m":"best of those proficient in the use of weapons"},{"d":"वरः","m":"foremost"},{"d":"मह्यद्युतिः","m":"endowed with great splendour"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"अस्त्रम्","m":"missile"},{"d":"गान्धर्वेण","m":"presided over by Gandharvas"},{"d":"परमास्त्रण","m":"supreme missiles"},{"d":"जघान","m":"neutralized"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"तस्मिन्प्रतिहतेऽतुराघवेणमहात्मना ।रावणःक्रोधाताम्राक्षस्सौरमस्त्रमुदैरयत्","trans":"When the missile of Ravana was turned void by the great selfRaghava, Ravana's eyes turned red in anger, and he used a missile presided over by the Sun God.","words":[{"d":"महात्मना","m":"great self"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"the aforesaid"},{"d":"अस्त्र","m":"missile"},{"d":"प्रतिहते","m":"turned void"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"सौरम् अस्त्रम्","m":"missile presided by sun god"},{"d":"उदैरयत्","m":"used"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"ततश्चक्राणिनिष्पेतुर्भास्वराणिमहान्ति च ।कार्मुकाद्भीमवेगस्यदशग्रीवस्यधीमतः","trans":"Thereafter, brilliant discus of the Sun God, issued forth from wise Ravana's bow at a terrific speed.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"भीमवेगस्य","m":"in terrific speed"},{"d":"धीमतः","m":"wise"},{"d":"दशग्रीवस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"कार्मुकात्","m":"bow"},{"d":"भास्वराणि","m":"of the sun god"},{"d":"महान्ति","m":"brilliant"},{"d":"चक्राणि","m":"discuses"},{"d":"निष्पेतुः","m":"issued forth"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"तैरासीद्गगनंदीप्तंसन्ततद्भिःरितस्ततः ।पतद्भिश्चदिशोदीप्ताश्चन्द्रसूर्यग्रहैरिव","trans":"As they landed together from the sky glowing like Sun, moon, and the planets, it illuminated the quarters.","words":[{"d":"सम्पतद्भिः","m":"together from the sky"},{"d":"पतद्भिश्च","m":"falling"},{"d":"तैः","m":"they"},{"d":"दीप्ता","m":"glowing"},{"d":"चन्द्रसूर्यग्रहैरिव","m":"like the moon sun and planets"},{"d":"गगनम्","m":"the sky"},{"d":"आसीत्","m":"illuminated"},{"d":"दिशश्च","m":"the quarters"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"तानिचिच्छेदबाणौघैश्चक्राणितु स राघवः ।आयुधानि च चित्राणिरावणस्यचमूमुखे","trans":"Raghava with his shafts shattered the discuses and the weapons of Ravana in the forefront of his army.","words":[{"d":"सःराघवः","m":"that Raghava"},{"d":"बाणौघैः","m":"shafts"},{"d":"तानि","m":"them"},{"d":"चक्राणि","m":"discuses"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"of Ravana"},{"d":"आयुधानि च","m":"and the weapons"},{"d":"चमूमुखे","m":"forefront of army"},{"d":"चिच्छेद","m":"shattered"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"तदस्त्रंतुहतंदृष्टवारावणोराक्षसाधिपः ।विव्याथदशभिर्बाणैरामंसर्वेषुमर्मसु","trans":"Rakshasa king, frustrated on seeing the missiles, pierced Rama in his private parts with shafts.","words":[{"d":"राक्षसाधिपः","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"अस्त्रम्","m":"missile"},{"d":"हतम्","m":"frustrated"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"दशभिः","m":"ten"},{"d":"बाणैः","m":"shafts"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"at Rama"},{"d":"सर्वेषु","m":"all sides"},{"d":"मर्मसु","m":"private parts"},{"d":"विव्याध","m":"pierced"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"स विद्धोदशभिर्बाणैर्महाकार्मुकनिस्सृतैः ।रावणेनमहातेजा न प्राकम्पतराघवः","trans":"Even though pierced by Ravana with ten arrows, Rama, endowed with high energy, was not shaken.","words":[{"d":"रावणेन","m":"by Ravana"},{"d":"महाकार्मुकनिस्सृतैः","m":"from the huge bow"},{"d":"दशभिः","m":"ten"},{"d":"बाणैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"विद्धः","m":"pierced"},{"d":"महातेजाः","m":"endowed with high energy"},{"d":"सःराघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"न प्राकम्पत","m":"not shaken"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"ततोविव्याथगात्रेषुसर्वेषुसमितिञ्जयः ।राघवस्तुसुसङ्क्रुद्धोरावणंबहुभिश्शरैः","trans":"Then, Raghava, who had won many battles, became highly furious, piercing Ravana in all his limbs with many arrows.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"समितिञ्जयः","m":"who won battles"},{"d":"राघवस्तु","m":"at Raghava"},{"d":"सुसङ्क्रुद्धः","m":"highly furious"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"बहुभिः","m":"many"},{"d":"शरैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"सर्वेषु","m":"all sides"},{"d":"गात्रेषु","m":"limbs"},{"d":"विव्याध","m":"pierced"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"एतस्मिन्नन्तरेक्रुद्धोराघवस्यानुजोबली ।लक्ष्मणःसायकान्सप्तजग्राहपरवीरहा","trans":"In the meantime, enraged Lakshmana, the brother of Rama, a mighty warrior, seized hold of seven shafts.","words":[{"d":"एतस्मिन्","m":"in the meantime"},{"d":"क्रुद्धः","m":"enraged"},{"d":"राघवस्य","m":"Raghava's"},{"d":"अनुजः","m":"brother"},{"d":"बली","m":"mighty"},{"d":"परवीरहा","m":"warrior"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणः","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"सप्त","m":"seven"},{"d":"सायकान्","m":"shafts"},{"d":"जग्राह","m":"seized"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"तै: स्सायकैर्महावेगैरावणस्यमहाद्युति ।ध्वजंमनुष्यशीर्षंतुतस्यचिच्छेदनैकधा","trans":"Lakshmana, who was endowed with extraordinary splendour, for his part, with his shafts which had great force, shattered the device of man's head on the flag post of Ravana.","words":[{"d":"महाद्युतिः","m":"endowed with extraordinary splendour"},{"d":"महावेगैः","m":"at high speed"},{"d":"तैःसायकैः","m":"those shafts"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"मनुष्यशीर्षम्","m":"device of human head"},{"d":"ध्वजम्","m":"flag post"},{"d":"नैकधा","m":"one"},{"d":"चिच्छेद","m":"shattered"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"सारदथेश्चापिबाणेनशिरोज्वलितकुण्डलम् ।जहारलक्ष्मणःश्रीमान्नैरृतस्यमहाबलः","trans":"Celebrated, mighty Lakshmana struck with his arrows, that hit the head of the charioteer of night ranger, which was glittering with earrings.","words":[{"d":"श्रीमान्","m":"celebrated"},{"d":"महाबलः","m":"mighty"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणः","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"बाणेन","m":"by the arrows"},{"d":"नैरृतस्य","m":"night ranger's"},{"d":"सारथेः","m":"charioteer"},{"d":"ज्वलितकुण्डलम्","m":"glittering earrings"},{"d":"शिरः","m":"head"},{"d":"जहार","m":"struck"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"तस्यबाणैश्चचिच्छेदधनुर्गजकरोपमम् ।लक्ष्मणोराक्षसेन्द्रस्यपञ्चभिर्निशितैस्तदा","trans":"Then Lakshmana split with five sharpened arrows the bow of Rakshasa king that resembled elephant's trunk.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणः","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"निशितैः","m":"sharpened"},{"d":"पञ्चभिः","m":"five"},{"d":"बाणैः","m":"arrows"},{"d":"तस्यराक्षसेन्द्रस्य","m":"that king of Rakshasa's"},{"d":"गजकरोपमम्","m":"resembling the trunk of elephant"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"चिच्छेद","m":"split"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"नीलमेघनिभांश्चास्यसदश्वान् पर्वतोपमान् ।जघानाप्लुत्यगदयारावणस्यविभीषणः","trans":"Vibheeshana struck with his formidable mace the horses of Ravana which were like dark clouds and huge like mountains.","words":[{"d":"विभीषणः","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"आप्लुत्य","m":"formidable"},{"d":"गदया","m":"with mace"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"नीलमेघनिभान्","m":"like dark cloud"},{"d":"पर्वतोपमान्","m":"like mountain"},{"d":"सदश्वान्","m":"his horses"},{"d":"जघाम","m":"struck"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"हताश्वात्त्तुस्वोवेगादवप्लुत्यमहारथात् ।कोपमाहारत्तीव्रंभ्रातरंप्रतिरावणः","trans":"With the horses of his chariot dead, Ravana descended from the huge chariot and exhibited violent rage against his brother.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"हताश्वात्","m":"dead horses"},{"d":"महारथात्","m":"huge chariot"},{"d":"वेगात्","m":"speedily"},{"d":"अवप्लुत्य","m":"descended"},{"d":"भ्रातरंप्रति","m":"against brother"},{"d":"तीव्रम्","m":"violent"},{"d":"कोपम्","m":"rage"},{"d":"आहारयत्","m":"exhibited"}]},{"v":19,"dev":"ततश्शक्तिंमहाशक्तिर्दीप्तार्दीप्ताशनीमिव ।विभीषणस्यचिक्षेपराक्षसेन्द्रःप्रतापवान्","trans":"Then, endowed with extraordinary energy, the powerful leader of Rakshasas hurled a flaming thunderbolt like javelin at Vibheeshana.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"महाशक्